              <p>Lisa Marie Crafts has one simple mission: Crafting to Create Happiness. The aim is to create bespoke personalised gifts that'll bring joy to loved ones and spread smiles across faces. Every craft is handmade and tailored to the individual, so no two are ever the same.</p> 
              <p>No matter what the occasion – whether it’s a loved one’s birthday, a best friend’s engagement, or a relative’s funeral – Lisa Marie Crafts will have you covered and deliver the perfect message and sentiment every time.</p>
